    Note over User,Safety: Flow 1: Remote Vulnerability Scan

    User->>LS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>Configurable Auth
    LS->>Remote: Dispatch to provider
    Remote->>KFP: Submit garak_scan_pipeline<br/>Bearer Token (HTTPS/TLS)
    KFP-->>Remote: Pipeline Run ID
    Remote-->>LS: Job ID (async)
    LS-->>User: Job ID

    Note over KFP,ParsePod: KFP Pipeline Execution (3-step DAG)

    KFP->>ValPod: Step 1: validate_inputs
    ValPod->>LS: Check connectivity<br/>HTTP/HTTPS Configurable
    LS-->>ValPod: OK
    ValPod-->>KFP: Validated

    KFP->>ScanPod: Step 2: garak_scan
    ScanPod->>vLLM: Probe requests (adversarial)<br/>API Key Auth
    vLLM-->>ScanPod: Model responses
    ScanPod->>Files: Upload report.jsonl<br/>HTTP/HTTPS Configurable
    ScanPod->>Files: Upload AVID report
    ScanPod->>Files: Upload HTML report
    ScanPod-->>KFP: Scan complete

    KFP->>ParsePod: Step 3: parse_results
    ParsePod->>Files: Download reports
    ParsePod->>Files: Upload combined EvaluateResponse
    ParsePod-->>KFP: Results parsed

    Note over User,LS: User polls for results

    User->>LS: GET /alpha/eval/jobs/status
    LS->>Remote: Check status
    Remote->>KFP: Get run state<br/>Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: Run status
    Remote-->>LS: Job status
    LS-->>User: Status (running/completed)

    User->>LS: GET /alpha/eval/get_eval_job_result
    LS->>Remote: Get results
    Remote->>Files: Retrieve combined results
    Files-->>Remote: EvaluateResponse
    Remote-->>LS: Results
    LS-->>User: Scan results (JSONL + AVID)

    Note over User,Safety: Flow 2: Shield Effectiveness Testing

    ScanPod->>Safety: Run input shields<br/>(Prompt-Guard-86M)
    Safety-->>ScanPod: Shield verdict
    ScanPod->>LS: Inference request (LLM)
    LS-->>ScanPod: LLM response
    ScanPod->>Safety: Run output shields
    Safety-->>ScanPod: Shield verdict
